{"id":"e9cce3e9-6a20-4e8c-a6e9-ce0d75d595e0","level":0,"callsign":"Vas","name":"Vasily Halladay","player_name":"","status":"ACTIVE","dead":false,"text_appearance":"","notes":"","history":"<p>Vasily Halladay grew up as an orphan together with his brother, Vincent, in a backwater colony in the barren planet of Urruk. The brothers took odd jobs just to support themselves. One day, Vasily managed to protect a little girl from a group of thugs. It turns out, this girl is the daughter of Alastair Shaw, an honoured wing of the Albatross. As repayment, Shaw offered to send him to a union core world to study to become a lancer. In exchange, he must serve the Albatross as one of their loyal wing under the newly formed makteba in Urruk. Promising to send Vincent messages whenever he gets the chance, Vasily sets off to one of the union core worlds to train to be a lancer.</p>","quirks":[],"current_hp":9,"background":"Soldier","resistances":[],"portrait":"","cloud_portrait":"https://ds69h3g1zxwgy.cloudfront.net/80714559-7bc6-43e2-89e1-d0e3094a90aa/images/1000070247.jpeg","group":"","sort_index":-1,"cc_ver":"","isDeleted":false,"expireTime":"","deleteTime":"","lastModified":"Sun May 03 2026 14:44:53 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)","lastUpdate_cloud":"Sun May 03 2026 14:44:53 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)","lastSync":"Sun May 03 2026 14:44:53 GMT+0800 (Philippine Standard Time)","skills":[{"id":"sk_assault","rank":1},{"id":"sk_blow_something_up","rank":1},{"id":"sk_show_off","rank":1},{"id":"sk_take_control","rank":1}],"talents":[{"id":"t_ace","rank":1},{"id":"t_duelist","rank":1},{"id":"t_juggernaut","rank":1}],"mechSkills":[0,2,0,0],"core_bonuses":[],"licenses":[],"reserves":[],"orgs":[],"counter_data":[],"custom_counters":[],"special_equipment":{"PilotGear":[],"Frames":[],"MechWeapons":[],"WeaponMods":[],"MechSystems":[]},"bondId":"","xp":0,"stress":0,"isBroken":false,"burdens":[],"bondPowers":[],"powerSelections":0,"maxStress":8,"bondAnswers":["",""],"minorIdeal":""